ğŸ§  Overview

The Shift Scheduler System is an enterprise web application developed for Doria, designed to centralize, organize, and optimize shift scheduling across all business areas.

It enhances operational control, visibility, and communication between managers and employees, providing a reliable and structured scheduling solution.

